Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,EMBODIED. Egocentric multimodal Marine training simulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM training modernization: instructor-to-trainee ratio is the\Nbottleneck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight egocentric scenarios — doorway, checkpoint, casualty, IED, night\Nperimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Each scenario is anchored to a doctrine reference — MCWP, MCRP, TM. No\Ninvention.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Trainee types their action. Multimodal coach reads the frame plus the\Nresponse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Vision-capable model classifies the action against doctrine.\NStructured JSON.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Score, doctrine cite, simulated consequence, coaching feedback — in\None shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After-action across attempts — a one-page Egocentric Decision Brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL — same code, trainee video stays inside the\Nwire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
